text: One you don't want to miss out on! Build your dream home this summer. Plans for modern design, high vaulted ceilings, 2, 000 sq ft, multiple decks and 4 bedrooms. Large windows and open-air concept make this home feel luxurious. Lot has Green-belt area to the rear of the property with a small creek. Nice separation between the houses below for a private feel. Very nice territorial view and setting from the property. Located in Gate 3 of Suden Valley, similar home plans have sold for $700K+ when finished.

Brand new townhome in Bellingham's Sunset Village community. This 3 story, 3 bedroom, 1.75 bath interior unit features an oversized garage, stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops & mixed cabinetry. Walkable to shopping, dining, bus line, & trail system. Don't miss out on a great opportunity!

Opportunity awaits for you to build sweat equity in this charming and affordable starter home in the Lettered Streets. 3 bedrooms and 1 full bath with a spacious kitchen featuring brand new flooring. The generously sized backyard features raised garden beds, a garden shed and a covered wood storage area. The hot water tank is only 4 years old. The roof, gutters and siding were recently cleaned (includes 1 and 2 year warranty). Seller offering a $6k credit (w/ full priced offers); use for rate buy down, bathroom remodel, or other upgrades to the home! Make this home yours today.

Welcome to Phase 2 of The Ridge in Blaine, WA! This stunning new home offers a spacious corner lot, ideal for maximizing outdoor living with covered areas in both front and back. Enjoy versatile living with two primary bedrooms on the main level, perfect for multi-generational living or a home office setup. The open, functional floorplan is designed for modern living, while the low-maintenance slab on grade foundation ensures convenience. Luxury Vinyl Flooring and quartz countertops with slab backsplash. The prime location is close to downtown Blaine and I-5, you'll have easy access to everything you need. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity! $5, 000 Buyer Credit with our preferred Lender, Becky Farrar at Evergreen Home Loans.

This home is in Drayton Reach where there are community beaches and grand salt water views. The newly constructed home is absolutely stunning and the floorplan is amazing. There are truly 2 large bedrooms, plus an office, with two spacious primary suites (one on each floor) AND two bonus rooms (which could make for additional bedrooms, if you wish)! The floor plan is open on the main floor with a spacious kitchen/dining/living area and all rooms have water views, except one bonus room and the powder room. This home was designed with the thought of multi-generational living, or those who work from home. The location is ideal with the community beaches, and short drive to downtown Blain and I-5. You need to see this gorgeous new home!

Beautifully maintained and updated custom home centrally located, close to the heart of downtown Lynden! Featuring 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and 2, 513sqft of living space. This open concept main floor living space features gas fireplace, kitchen with cherry cabinets, granite counters and large island overlooking the dining and living spaces. Expansive primary suite with updated custom bathroom. Tons of natural light and brand-new interior paint throughout! As you head upstairs you will find 2 more bedrooms, a bathroom and a great bonus room to entertain! Take a step outside and enjoy the tranquil oversized back yard featuring an amazing patio, rope swing, gardening space/shed, fire pit and a hot tub! Added bonus- all new exterior paint!

Unlock the potential on this Alabama Hill View Ridge neighborhood fixer. Huge 14, 000sf mostly flat lot with partial city and bay views. 1 level rambler with daylight basement, great bones to work with. Needs a complete remodel top to bottom. Newer roof and Hardie Plank siding already completed. Total home square footage is around 2, 000. Very desirable neighborhood. Sunny, light and bright.

This light and bright Pacific NW Contemporary style home has all of the ideal features youve been looking for! Enter into your great rm, complete with vaulted ceilings and stone fireplace, and head into your spacious kitchen w/ hardwood floors, granite counter tops, and a large island with eating space. Relax in your roomy primary bdrm and enjoy the en-suite with glassed-in shower. Your back deck & covered porch are the perfect places to take in the fresh landscaping and stunning sunset views! A newer roof, hot water heater, 2 car garage, and flat driveway are just some of the extra perks of this lovely property. Enjoy all SV amenities; golf course, gym, swimming pools, tennis courts, trails, boat launch and 24/hour security.

Single story home on a large lot. 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom, excellent layout. Step out onto the deck and enjoy the huge backyard with mature trees. Bring this home back to life with a little sweat equity, and make it your own! Walking distance to schools, dining and other amenities.

Combining quiet seclusion w/ modern elegance, this gorgeous 4-bed/3.5-bath home sits on an enchanting 2.5-acre lot near Lake Whatcom. Main level feat. easy flow between office, living/dining rooms, + open kitchen w quartz counters, SS appliances, walk-in pantry, + large island w bar seating. Upstairs boasts stunning primary w/ fireplace + giant en-suite bath w soaking tub, dual vanities, + huge shower. 3 guest beds, 2.5 guest baths, bonus room, + laundry on both levels complete the picture. Greenbelt cloaks fenced back yard in peace + natural splendor, creating an oasis perfect for relaxing, entertaining, or retreating from the world. Plus: attached 2-car garage + tons of parking. Space + serenity in one beautiful property. Welcome home!

Come see the potential of this charming 2 bed 1 bath home in Bellingham's coveted Columbia district! Enjoy short walks to the nearby parks schools and beaches with easy access to local amenities and downtown. The 3rd bedroom has been cleverly converted into a dining room with an open kitchen concept that makes the most of its space. Enjoy the expansive patio and front yard, perfect for outdoor gathering and entertaining. Additionally the detached garage offers ample room for a workshop or parking, with driveway space for an RV or boat. Plenty of room for personalization and enhancement, the possibilities are endless. Don't miss this opportunity to live in desirable Bellingham neighborhood.

First time on the market! Don't miss this well loved 3-bedroom home with original features including beautiful hardwood floors and a wood burning fireplace. The 1.65 acre property also features a large carport and a huge shop! The property is zoned for Light Impact Industrial, which provides many options...run your business in the shop and live in the house, live in the home and benefit from the appreciation in the land with this valuable zoning, or develop the property. This part of Bellingham is seeing lots of growth with the new Costco, nearby multi-family developments, and easy access to I-5 and the Airport.

This remarkable home offers a comfortable living space featuring 4 beds and 2.5 baths. Inside, you'll find vaulted ceilings in both the living room and dining areas. floor-to-ceiling custom fireplace, open floor plan, spacious kitchen w/ island, pantry, mudroom, and laundry area, primary bedroom on the main floor w/walk-in closet. Other notable features of this property include a covered front porch, an entry closet, and a 2-car garage. Step outside onto the covered back porch w/ a privacy wall for those who love outdoor entertaining, perfect for year-round gatherings. Don't miss out on this opportunity. House plan model - Lexington. This home is Move In Ready!

Discover modern comfort in this 2-bed, 1.5-bath Blaine condominium. Enjoy townhouse-style living with a garage and additional parking. Move-in ready, with all appliances included, including washer/dryer. Only minutes from downtown, this cozy retreat offers convenience and charm! Close to grocery store and amenities of Blaine. Great proximity to the truck crossing for our northern neighbors. Super quiet, great walking areas and just a super property to call home. No rental cap so investors delight.

Downtown Blaine living and prime location near restaurants and parks. Easy access to the Canadian Border and I-5. Almost 15, 000 sqft level lot complete with fully fenced yard, large concrete patio and grass backyard - a great area for gardening! Main floor living home includes a spacious two-car garage with workshop area. Inside, enjoy a large living room with fireplace and hardwood floors, three bedrooms, and a partially finished daylight basement with separate entrance for potential income or future living space. While this home may need a touch of TLC and some sweat equity, the potential is undeniable. With great bones and a fantastic location, this property is waiting for the right owner to unlock its full potential and make it shine!

This adorable home is located in the Cornwall Park neighborhood just across the street from the Cornwall Rose Garden and centrally located near shopping, restaurants, downtown Bellingham, and easy I-5 access. This 3 bedroom 1.75 bathroom home features main level living with the 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom on the main level and 1 bedroom and .75 bathroom on the lower level. The home has been renovated to include fresh exterior and interior paint, updated kitchen with quartz counter tops, cabinets, and new appliances, updated bathrooms, beautiful hardwood floors, and new flooring throughout. This move-in ready home is waiting for your finishing touches.
neighborhoods: Broadway Park Historic District, Cornwall Park

text: This beautiful lot has the potential to build your peaceful home or cabin with great views of Toad Lake. Huge majestic trees stand tall for privacy or clear to expand your view or the lake. Envision building your ideal cabin with sweeping decks to expand your outdoor living and embrace the serenity of tranquil surroundings and lake view. This ideal location with ease of access to Bellingham makes this a desired location. Access to this lot can be from Emerald lake way or Sleepy Hollow Lane.Bring your imagination to embrace all the opportunities.

Remarkable Latitude 49 is the premier Birch Bay gated, all ages community. 365 days/year, beach-chic turnkey home can become a full-time or vacation residence. #266 is centrally located near the clubhouse & pool. Superbly maintained & stylish manu home is 565 SF, has 2 BR & 1 full BA built in 1998. Lots of windows & fully furnished w/ a spacious & sunny deck. A solid outbuilding behind the home. Latitude 49 has outdoor pool (new reno!), clubhouse, exercise room, athletic courts, & more. Near all the fun of Birch Bay beaches, less than five minutes away - sandy beaches, swimming, low tides, paddleboarding, clamming, crabbing, restaurants, festivals & all within the golf cart zone. Welcome to Latitude 49!

Welcome to your new home in the heart of Bellingham's beloved Sunnyland neighborhood! Located on a large lot with alley access, on a quiet, tree lined street. This is truly a rare find! Step into this well crafted Kenoyer-built home and discover the epitome of timeless elegance and modern comfort. From the charming curb appeal to the thoughtful interior layout, every detail exudes quality in craftsmanship. This home has had every upgrade that matters, including a new roof, plumbing and electrical. Conveniently located near parks, schools, shopping, and dining, this home offers the best of Bellingham living. Don't miss your opportunity to experience the unparalleled quality and charm of this home, on one of the best streets in town.

BRAND NEW!!!! One-of-a-kind, 2 bedroom cottage in the Sunset Village neighborhood is one you won't want to miss! Featuring an open concept first floor living space & kitchen that includes quartz countertops and SS appliances. A powder bath and back patio finish out the first floor. Upstairs includes two good sized bedrooms and a full size bathroom. This cottage come with a designated parking area & a private storage unit for bikes, outdoor furniture or any other storage you may need. Call today if interested!

You'll have no trouble envisioning life in this gem. Prime Everson location outside of the flood zone--flood-free history! Right away, you'll have to take a second glance to realize this isn't new construction. Fresh paint, new gutters, landscaping give it a crisp look. With ample garden space, a custom fire pit area, and a large storage shed, outdoor living is a breeze. Inside, you'll be wowed at the perfectly remodeled primary bedroom w/ a custom craftsman wall. Living room anchored by a hand-made concrete hearth and Douglas Fir wraparound mantle. Kitchen is fresh! Big costs done: new furnace and water heater. Located near schools and downtown, you legitimately get to live away from things but have community nearby if you desire.

Bright, airy, spacious AND on a double lot! This gorgeous home boasts a beautiful open floor plan, vaulted ceilings, windows overlooking the towering pines & stunning skylights that bring the great PNW outdoors in! Built with entertaining in mind, this home has ample room for multiple cooks in the kitchen + eating bar, get-togethers on the back deck & a finished lower level media room w/its own entrance, wet bar, full bath & 2 extra bedrooms. When youre not hosting, enjoy single level living on your main floor where you can relax in your oversized primary suite w/attached full bath, walk-in closet & private slider to the deck. Add'l features include a cozy gas fireplace, vaulted ceilings, quiet cul-de-sac location and playground nearby.

Water view home with a nice amenity package. Newer primary bath, ductless mini split system, free standing gas stove, detached two car garage, RV parking, newer hot tub, and a golf course, pool, and tennis court, just a few steps away. Easy care laminate flooring and a breakfast bar in the kitchen. Private fenced area with a hot tub and another fenced sitting area in the front of the home. Easy 10 minute drive to Ferndale and 20 minutes to Bellingham.

Must see this remarkable custom built home in Sudden Valley's coveted Gate 1! This unique house is a fantastic find in the picturesque setting of gorgeous Lake Whatcom with stunning views of the lake and an almost half acre lot to call your own. Frank Lloyd Wright inspired home features two story high ceilings and floor to ceiling windows letting in the natural light and providing views of the lake and surrounding forest from every room. Primary suite offers it's own balcony as well as lots of space, a huge walk-in closet and a spa sized bath. Huge flat driveway with a spacious 3 car garage. Sudden Valley offers a plethora of amenities including a marina and lake front dog park, both in Gate 1! Home also has an emergency generator!

Lake view sunsets from your expansive deck are beckoning! Perched directly across from Lake Whatcom on a private dead end road this 5 bed/4.5 bath 4, 384 sqft custom built home offers you quintessential PNW comfort & views. Enjoy true main floor living, vaulted ceilings, oak flooring and expansive deck & patio. Each spacious main floor bedroom features an ensuite, with the primary suite overlooking the lake. The daylight basement lives large with 2 bedrooms, a full bath, living room and 850sqft of flex space. Enjoy all that Lake Whatcom has to offer you with new views everyday and nearby public beach access within a short walk or bike ride. Don't miss out, see this one in person!

Tastefully updated mid century modern home with incredible views of the Mountain's, Islands & Bellingham Bay. Natural light filters thru large picture windows and the doors. The panoramic views are ever changing. Adjacent to the home is a detached studio offering many options for a quiet space, creativity, and relaxation. A tranquil goldfish pond with waterfall creates a beautiful focal point in the yard. The flagstone walkway is surrounded by colorful perennials, trees and ferns. Evenings can be enjoyed dining al fresco in the gazebo with string lights overhead, and later on there's stargazing on the deck off the kitchen and living room. Add your own rooftop garden over the spacious 2 car garage. The sunsets here are spectacular!

This beautifully maintained zero-steps home features 3 beds & 2 baths with a 2 car garage. The open concept layout offers newer laminate flooring, gas fireplace, vaulted ceilings, soaker tub, & granite countertops. Enjoy the sun on your large private deck, and cool off indoors with A/C. The furnace is brand new and all appliances were replaced in 2021. The community clubhouse is nearby and offers a kitchen, library, and community mailboxes. The neighborhood is very walkable and close to so many amenities including a major bus route, Cordata Park, trails for walking, shopping centers, restaurants, and medical facilities. The wonderfully managed 55+ Cordate Park Place HOA takes care of all exterior finishes including landscaping!

Irongate RediSpace - State of the art industrial/storage condominiums conveniently located in the Irongate Industrial Business Park. This is not your typical storage garage. Quality built with steel construction and metal roofs for longevity and low maintenance in mind, and a gated community that is secure and accessible 24/7. Designed with style in mind and extra wide 70-foot aisle ways between buildings for easy maneuverability for most any vehicle. Features include an ADA bathroom, large 14x14 overhead doors with windows and automated openers, 75, 000 BTU natural gas heater, high vaulted ceilings, 150-amp 3 phase power, wired for communication, personal mailbox and so much more. Why rent when you can own...A SPACE THAT'S ALL YOURS!

Private paradise & a tranquil retreat to explore on your forested 6+ acres! 2912sqft home has vaulted ceilings w/ numerous windows to allow for beautiful natural lighting! Open kitchen and a deck overlooking a small creek. 3 bedrooms & 2.75 bathrooms. Don't miss the Finished daylight basement suite complete w/ a murphy bed, washer /dryer and an outside entrance. Private deck off the primary bedroom to enjoy a breathtaking view of your own park! Close to Lake Padden and world class Mountain Biking at Galbraith Mountain.

Endless options! Many uses for this home. Live in 1 and rent the other, rent both or easily combine them to create 1 home. Currently the home is divided into 2 residences with seperate entrances and private yards. The upper home is 2 levels and is approx 1747 sq ft. The downstairs is approx 867 sq ft. Large paved driveway leads to 2 outbuildings. One has a shop and an additional .5 bath. Enjoy your private fenced back yard which includes an established garden, above ground pool and hottub. Recent improvements include new paint and flooring downstairs, new exterior paint and fairly new roof with solar panels. Just shy of half of an acre and close to town. Located across the street from the elementary school.

BUILDERS & AMBITIOUS REMODELERS! AS-IS Fixer or Easily Buildable Lot 1/4 mile from Whole Foods. Take advantage of the connection & impact fees already paid when you buy this major-remodel-or-just-tear-it-down home on a flat, buildable 4792 sq. ft. lot. Excellent, convenient location in the Puget Neighborhood. High rental demand & accessible location + the upcoming HB 1110 zoning law changes throughout Washington, can combine to create a lucrative multifamily building opportunity by early 2026. Buyer to verify. Located in the public schools attendance areas of Carl Cozier Elementary, Kulshan Middle School & Sehome High. Some MAY see a remodel opportunity, while others may see a tear-down. Either way: Opportunity is knocking!

Fantastic mid-county location for under $500K that checks so many boxes! Situated in a cul-de-sac on a large lot, this warm and inviting 4 bedroom/1.75 bathroom home features new luxury vinyl flooring, carpet, interior doors, front door, garage door, roof, water heater and exterior paint. Adaptable floor plan with 2 bedrooms up + 2 bedrooms down. Attached 2 car garage plus in home laundry area. The 11K+ square foot private lot is the ideal space to relax or entertain. Quick and easy I-5 access has you in Bellingham or Blaine in 10 minutes. This price point is rapidly disappearing and finding a flexible no HOA neighborhood can also be a challenge...don't miss this one!

Stunning updated craftsman with historical charm, this 3-story, nearly 3, 000 SF home includes 4 beds, 2.5 baths, & space for a home office, library, &/or playroom. Originally built in 1907, moved to the property & fully renovated in 1999, & updated again in 2022, this property's seamless blend of modern and historical features make it one of a kind. It includes refinished fir floors, custom steelwork, woodwork, built-ins, & ample natural light from south-facing windows, & skylights. Fresh exterior paint, a level backyard, patio, & garden beds, surrounded by beautiful landscaping, including fruit trees. Gorgeous sunsets with partial views of Orcas & the Bay can be seen from the main & upper floors. EV-charging station & direct trail access.

Escape to your slice of paradise amidst stunning vistas and original charm. This picturesque property offers level pastures and river access, perfect for hobbyists and nature enthusiasts alike. Discover versatile outbuildings, including a detached garage & workshop, a spacious barn, a charming cottage, adorable greenhouse, enhancing the property's unique allure. Step inside the main residence to find a well-appointed kitchen, a spacious dining room with a bay window, and a welcoming living room. Practical features include a walk-in pantry and a mudroom with a full-size washer/dryer. This estate is a rare find, blending tranquility with investment potential. Don't miss the chance to make it your own endless possibilities!

Nestled in the serene Birchwood neighborhood, this 3 bed, 2.5 bath home on corner lot offers a blend of comfort and modern amenities. Entry features built-ins for ample storage. Walk in to open main floor w/ new LVP floors and a galley kitchen w/ stainless appliances & granite counters. Enjoy the comfort & efficiency of ductless Mini/Split. Step upstairs to large primary suite w/ 2 large closets and primary bath that includes large shower and plenty of counter space. 2 additional bedrooms upstairs. 2 car garage. Enjoy outdoors in beautifully landscaped, newly fenced yard with a private patio, grassy area & raised beds in the front yard. With direct trail access in the back, this home is joggable to Squalicum Park, Squalicum Beach, and more.

Welcome Home to this one-level, ground-floor condo w/attached garage, all updated & ready for your move-in! Or, invest and RENT IT OUT! Remodel just completed w/new flooring, paint, & fixtures. Primary Suite w/full bath & large walk-in closet + guest BR & 2nd full bath. Cozy gas-log fireplace in the family room, forced air heat, gas range, full-size washer/dryer included. You'll appreciate the extra-clean 1-car garage for storage or dry, secure parking & includes new opener. Blocks from Whatcom Falls Park & minutes to Barkley Village, making this the perfect -- & affordable -- home to base your Pacific NW Way of Life - or add to your rental portfolio! Dues include water, sewer, garbage, recycling, internet, cable, & common area maintenance.

Welcome to this gorgeous contemporary single-level home in Birch Bay, just a half mile from the Point Whithorn Reserve and a mile from Birch Bay State Park. This beautiful home boasts bay vistas and features vaulted ceilings, expansive floor to ceiling windows, deluxe vinyl plank flooring, luxe leather finish granite countertops and stainless appliances. The spacious and airy layout is perfect for enjoying the salt water views from nearly every room in the house. A wonderful large deck off the main living area and a large flat yard, retaining wall and low maintenance landscaping frame the home outside. No HOA!

Affordable saltwater view condo with a just-completed 2023 remodel. New kitchen, bathrooms, and interior remodeling. Enjoy ocean views from primary, living room, and kitchen. Access to gated beach, including paddle board/kayak storage. Steps to in-ground pool, and close parking. Ample attic storage. HOA $325/month includes: water, sewer, garbage, flood insurance, snow removal & exterior maintenance. Rental potential of $1975/month or more (3 month minimum rental). With ocean views, modern upgrades, and unbeatable location, this condo offers a seaside lifestyle, or great investment potential. This condo checks all the boxes.

Outdoor enthusiasts rejoice! Nestled w/in Gate 3 & surrounded by trees, this 4 bed 2.5 bath home welcomes you w/its spacious open concept. Picturesque windows and skylights allow the home to be drenched w/natural light. 3 beds on the main including primary w/ensuite. Designed w/entertainment in mind. Kitchen, living & dining room flow seamlessly to your wrap around deck, overlooking your low maintenance yard & Little Strawberry Park. Downstairs (remodeled 2024) provides a multi-generational living option w/a second primary suite, living area and separate entrance. New roof (2019) provides peace of mind. Amenities include trails, parks, private beaches, 18 hole golf course, marina and seasonal pool. This home is your tranquil setting.

Introducing your ultimate sanctuary on Eliza Island! This exquisite, fully-equipped cabin embodies the essence of island living. With furnishings included - even a golf cart and dinghy - this turnkey haven powered by solar energy is ready for your enjoyment. Nestled on a high-bank waterfront lot, the property offers breathtaking views and beach trail access from several points points around the island. Inside, the cabin accommodates up to 10 guests with 3 bedrooms and a cozy loft. Stay warm by the fireplace or with propane wall heaters and a wood stove. Embrace the tranquility of your private escape, away from the chaos. Seize the chance to own a piece of paradise in the San Juan Islands. Bring your boat, take the watertaxi or fly-in.

Welcome to Falcon Landing! Located on the first lot in this new neighborhood in Everson, this home features a large open layout, 4 bed, 3 bathrooms plus a bonus room with 2435 sq/ft of living space. Modern design finishes throughout the home include a shiplap fireplace, laminate flooring, and hard surface countertops. The home has great garage space and 9 foot ceilings throughout the main floor! Call for your showing today!

Chuckanut Bay and Island view residence perched on an expansive, private 1.93 acre lot with spectacular views of the Bay and the San Juan Islands. Inviting sun-filled interiors offer a traditional floor plan highlighting the stunning westerly views. Culinary kitchen with granite countertops and Stainless appliances. Age in place with a guest bedroom + full bath on the main floor. Primary with endless views and a private balcony. Family room/yoga room with pocket French doors. Detached Accessory Dwelling with a spacious garage, storage, living space, kitchenette + bath. Interurban Trail access leads to charming Fairhaven historic district, Larrabee State Park + beaches. Embrace the natural beauty of the PNW lifestyle and place to call home.

Discover serene living at 4566 South Pass Rd, a beautifully updated home perched above Nooksack Valley. Just minutes from shopping and services but with a feeling of being far from everything. Enjoy mountain views, privacy, and modern comfort in this completely updated (2018) home that feels brand new. Features laminate flooring, a cozy wood stove, efficient heat pump, and a spacious primary suite. Ideal for nature lovers or as a tranquil second home. Features include two bedroom, one and 3/4 bath and a stand alone den/office and handicap ramp to side door. Bonus: RV parking spot with connections and stand alone building with kitchenet, toilet and bath. Embrace your new lifestyle in this picturesque retreat. Contact us for a viewing!

NEW CONSTRUCTION! If youve been searching for a beautifully designed home with thoughtful features and stunning finishes, look no further! Complete with a spacious layout, primary bedroom on the main, rec room, and huge office that could function as 3rd bedroom, youll have plenty of space for hosting and entertaining. Enjoy your cozy fireplace and ample natural light or take in the impeccably designed landscaping outdoors on your Trex back deck or covered porch. Located in the beautiful Glenhaven community, enjoy all the amenities this area has to offer. This home is a must-see!

Stunning full scribed log home nestled in the trees on Galbraith Mountain. World class mountain biking right out your back door yet only 10 minutes to downtown Bellingham. This shy 5 acre property offers the best of both worlds. The main level features a dramatic living room with cathedral ceilings and wall of windows, massive kitchen/dining room with rustic wood floors, bedroom, full bath, & utility room. Upstairs is a loft utilized as the primary bed, full bath, & 2nd bed with its own private balcony. In the daylight basement youll find a bedroom and large rec room with bath - potential for multi generational living. This exquisite home has undergone a full log restoration with warranty, as well as a new back deck, furnace, & carpet.

By the Sea, we have all dreamed of living next to it, hearing its waves, and the songs of the shorebirds that bring peace & tranquility that we so much need in our lives! So, here is your chance to own a rare Point Whitehorn waterfront home! Located south of Birch Bay State Park, and north of the Pt Whitehorn Marine Reserve, this home was designed to encompass salt-water views from virtually every room. An entertainer's dream, with a great-room, kitchen, and dining area that all continue out to a multi-level waterside deck. If you love the outdoors, your biking, running, or hiking day starts at the front door, and ends next to the sea as you watch the sunset over the bay that is just a stone's throw away from what could be your new home!

Welcome home! This beautiful lakefront property is just what youve been waiting for. With many desirable features, including private porches adorning both upstairs bedrooms, custom plumbed BBQ area and a private dock with hydraulic boat lift. This is lakeside living at its finest. The large covered deck with a beautiful lake view and hot tub is the perfect place to wind down and relax! Its ideal for entertaining guests year-round. This meticulously maintained home is ready to enjoy, and the enclosed garage offers the structural potential for a second-story addition. Positioned conveniently close to downtown and Barkley Village, and walkability to the Silver Beach Market and slow traffic along the lakeside main road.

Beautiful new construction home with a large yard and fantastic garage space. The home backs up to conservation woodlands that make for great scenery. The main floor is an open floorplan with a large island and plenty of cabinet space. The upstairs has three large bedrooms with lots of natural light. The main bathroom upstairs has a large vanity and the master bath is located off the master bedroom. The house boasts a 50-year membrane roofing system, fireplace, tankless water heater, and mini split heating and cooling.

Well-maintained Craftsman home on a large, level, private & fenced lot in North Prairie. Beautifully-landscaped yard backs to mature conifers on adjacent property. Main floor Primary suite with tiled shower, dual sinks, and walk-in closet. Open concept living/dining/kitchen with Costco-size walk-in pantry, granite countertops and tile backsplash. Bring the outdoors in with the 3-panel sliding door opening to the stamped concrete patio under the cover of a tongue & groove vaulted ceiling. Main floor office with French doors. Upstairs, you'll find 2 additional bedrooms, 3/4 bathroom, loft, and a 234 SQFT bonus room. No HOA.

This is the fixer opportunity you've been looking for! Situated on a double lot just a stone's throw from Lake Whatcom this property offers instant equity in a neighborhood of million-dollar homes. Lake views from the composite deck off the living room with fireplace. 2 bedrooms on the main level + an unfinished basement with potential for another bonus room/office and living room. Lower level also has a fireplace and half bathroom. Functional 2-car garage is great for projects & storage. Additional parking for cars, boats or RVs. Public beach access just down the street you can walk to to enjoy the lake!

Explore affordable, ground-level living in this charming 2BR/1.75BA condo in Bellingham! The unit features modern flooring, updated bathrooms, and a cozy gas fireplace. The large kitchen offers lots of counter space and cabinet storage. Spacious bedrooms include walk-in closets. Enjoy your peaceful covered back patio adjacent to Bellingham Country Club. Community amenities such as a fitness center and clubhouse, ideal for parties and gatherings. Minutes from downtown, Costco, major shopping, and I-5 for easy commuting. The perfect combination of location, quality, and affordability all wrapped into one little gem. Come see it before it's gone!

Attractive townhouse-style home in the popular Pinewood Hills neighborhood off Lakeway Dr. in Bellingham. Partial shake siding. Front entry is a solarium type room with spectacular view over the city (night view with lights!) and distant mountains of Canadian Coastal range on a sunny day. Skylights, interesting architecture. 1, 362 SF on two levels, 3 BR, 1.5 BA. Built 1996. 1-car garage and one parking space in driveway. There is an additional parking space in front of the home. Fully fenced backyard. Room for landscaping and gardens. Near the trail leading to greater area trailway system. A little Lakeway Dr. noise. Less than 5 minutes to I-5 Lakeway Exit - Fred Meyer & Market, restaurants, Woods Coffee, banks, shopping, public transit.

Here is an incredible opportunity to own a well cared for 4-plex in the desirable Lettered Streets neighborhood! Situated perfectly with trail access out the front door, a great walk & bike score + 4 parking spots! Two 2 bedroom, 1 bath units and two Studios with shared deck access. Many thoughtful updates throughout such as a newer roof, interior and exterior paint, updated bathrooms, newer carpet, and new appliances, as well as new recessed lighting and wall heaters throughout. All units include dishwashers and in-unit laundry! WOW! Proximity to restaurants, a yoga studio, parks, and more! An overall great building with excellent rental history!
